successes.title: Flyte:  Levitating Light
successes.description: Flyte is a levitating lightbulb powered through the air.

Pledges.description: We'll post your name on our backers list and keep you informed of the latest updates. Thanks again. HIGH FIVE !

Levitate anything! Make your own levitating creation. Great for creative light displays. The Flyte Maker Kit includes a base, magnet embedded with 4 LEDs and power adapter. Light is powered through the air via induction. No batteries required. Levitate any object up to 200 grams/ 7 ounces.

Early bird gets the worm! Your very own Flyte 1st run production. Be the first to get your hands on the most amazing lightbulb ever. Completely assembled. Completely ultimate! Includes lightbulb, AC Adaptor, and wooden base in your choice of ash, oak or walnut.
No batteries required.
